org.skyscreamer.nevado.jms.util

Class MarshallingSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.skyscreamer.nevado.jms.util.MarshallingSupport

  • public class MarshallingSupport
extends Object
    The fixed version of the UTF8 encoding function. Some older JVM's UTF8 encoding function breaks when handling large strings.
    Version:
    $Revision$
